{"title":"Sure Blade","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Sure_Blade","type":"markdown","data":"***Obsolete**: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.*\n\n| [![Sure blade.png](/images/7/72/Sure_blade.png)](/File:Sure_blade.png) Sure Blade |                                                                        |\n| :-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Level                                                                             | 2                                                                      |\n| School1                                                                           | [Hexes](/Hexes \"Hexes\")                                                |\n| School2                                                                           | [Charms](/Charms \"Charms\")                                             |\n| Source(s)                                                                         | - [Book of Maledictions](/Book_of_Maledictions \"Book of Maledictions\") |\n| [Casting noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")                                       | 2                                                                      |\n| [Spell noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")                                         | 0                                                                      |\n\n|   |                                                                                                                     |\n| - | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | This spell forms a mystical bond between the caster and a wielded short blade, making the blade much easier to use. |\n\n**Sure Blade** is a level 2 [Hexes](/Hexes \"Hexes\")/[Charms](/Charms \"Charms\") spell which temporarily adds +5 to +15 [accuracy](/Accuracy#Post-Roll \"Accuracy\") to all attacks with your currently wielded [short blade](/Short_blade \"Short blade\"). It has no impact on any other weapon type. The size of this accuracy bonus is dependent on the remaining duration of the spell, which is determined by [spell power](/Spell_power \"Spell power\"). Casting it repeatedly will also extend the duration, however. While short blades are already very accurate, this is a fairly cheap spell, and missing less often means fewer turns wasted in combat. Sure Blade's effect ends immediately if you unwield the affected weapon for any reason.\n\n## History\n\nIn [0.17](/0.17 \"0.17\") this spell was removed.\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Sure Blade - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Sure_Blade\",\"wgTitle\":\"Sure Blade\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":38910,\"wgRevisionId\":38910,\"wgArticleId\":431,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"Obsolete articles\",\"Hexes Spells\",\"Charms Spells\",\"Level 2 Spells\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPage