r: 1px solid #f00; background-color: #fcc; border-left: 15px solid #f00; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Obsolete</b>: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.</i></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 1.4em; margin-top:0; margin-right:0; padding: 0px; float: right; border:none;\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"border:none; margin:0; padding:0; width:18em;\">\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"> <a href=\"/File:Sure_blade.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Sure blade.png\" src=\"/images/7/72/Sure_blade.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#8195;Sure Blade\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Level\n</th>\n<td> 2\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>1</sup>\n</th>\n<td> <a href=\"/Hexes\" title=\"Hexes\">Hexes</a>\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>2</sup>\n</th>\n<td> <a href=\"/Charms\" title=\"Charms\">Charms</a>\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Source(s)\n</th>\n<td><div>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Book_of_Maledictions\" title=\"Book of Maledictions\">Book of Maledictions</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Casting noise</a>\n</th>\n<td> 2\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Spell noise</a>\n</th>\n<td> 0\n</td></tr>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</table></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> This spell forms a mystical bond between the caster and a wielded short blade, making the blade much easier to use.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Sure Blade</b> is a level 2 <a href=\"/Hexes\" title=\"Hexes\">Hexes</a>/<a href=\"/Charms\" title=\"Charms\">Charms</a> spell which temporarily adds +5 to +15 <a href=\"/Accuracy#Post-Roll\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Accuracy\">accuracy</a> to all attacks with your currently wielded <a href=\"/Short_blade\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Short blade\">short blade</a>. It has no impact on any other weapon type. The size of this accuracy bonus is dependent on the remaining duration of the spell, which is determined by <a href=\"/Spell_power\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Spell power\">spell power</a>. Casting it repeatedly will also extend the duration, however. While short blades are already very accurate, this is a fairly cheap spell, and missing less often means fewer turns wasted in combat. Sure Blade's effect ends immediately if you unwield the affected weapon for any reason.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/0.17\" title=\"0.17\">0.17</a> this spell was removed.\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916225836\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.060 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.082 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 135/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 683/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1681/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 398/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.010s\nLua virtual size: 8.14 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   64.192      1 -total\n 95.84%   61.520      1 Template:Spell\n 79.20%   50.838      8 Template:If\n  2.57%    1.648      1 Template:Charms\n  2.18%    1.402      1 Template:Hexes\n  1.90%    1.218      1 Template:Flavour\n  1.72%    1.106      1 Template:Obsolete\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:431-0!canonical and timestamp 20240916225836 and revision id 38910\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<di